 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/T%E1%BB%87-c%E1%BA%A9u-1/poem-tw2egnsMNYQ32ngMmJbGjw">Tệ cẩu 1 - 敝笱 1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/V%E1%BB%8B-minh-ti%E1%BB%83u-k%E1%BB%87-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-Phan-sinh-d%E1%BA%A1-to%E1%BA%A1/poem-NxGml8-WzETg66w1m_itcA">Vị minh tiểu kệ đồng Phan sinh dạ toạ - 味茗小偈同潘生夜坐</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/V%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BA%A7n-Xuy%C3%AAn/poem-XsprZk9IwJEYrOEpRQQrFQ">Vọng Tần Xuyên - 望秦川</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/author-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
